keyFacts: The document is a deed transferring property at 9 East 71st Street, New York, from Birch Wathen School, Inc. to Nine East 71st Street Corporation.
The transfer is executed in accordance with a New York Supreme Court Order dated February 6, 1989 (index No. 2225/89).
The property is described as a 50 by 102 foot parcel on the north side of 71st Street, east of 5th Avenue.
The deed includes standard covenants regarding liens and the application of consideration for improvements.
The recorded deed was to be mailed to attorney Jack S. Levey at a law firm in Columbus, Ohio.
